    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>Using Shortoce [idt_testimonial_display] in page to display testimonial in your page or post</p>\n<h3>From within WordPress</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Visit &#8216;Plugins &gt; Add New&#8217;</li>\n<li>Search for &#8216;IDT testimonial&#8217;</li>\n<li>Activate IDT testimonial Plugin from your Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>Manually</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Upload the <code>idt-testimonial-plugin</code> folder to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> directory</li>\n<li>Activate the IDT testimonial Plugin plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "installation": "<p>This section describes how to install the plugin and get it working.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Upload the plugin files to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/idt-testimonial-plugin</code> directory, or install the plugin through the WordPress plugins screen directly.</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; screen in WordPress</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial Release of IDT testimonial Plugin.</li>\n</ul>\n"
    },
